Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失的村庄的受害者被送往那个研究设施
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通称「{\1c&H000000\3c&HFFFFFF\bord2}工厂{\r}」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说要赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但去那里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出CIA和「{\1c&H0000FF}蛇{\r}」勾结的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告发相关者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但会这么顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「{\1c&H000000\3c&HFFFFFF\bord2}花园计划{\r}」若被公诸于世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府也没法无视被害者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必也能弄到药
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芸芸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你真正的名字是{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}绝望{\r}」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}绝望{\r}？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南完全没有绝望的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭吃的不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,属于丰满健康的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部再丰满点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波霸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点紧张感都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我感觉就这样也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止被外人觉察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然挖通遗迹内部修建设施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好夸张的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望入侵路线和我在时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一件武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防身用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我等成老太婆怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在接受姐姐大人的疼爱之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你做防老化处理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你一生不会变老
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来还在使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方是故意门户大开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要破坏一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多已经在设施里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人的话不能尽信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多应该没有撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到她的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颜色？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的感觉恢复了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都看不到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样 已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:06:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在上海协助逃亡的「花苞」还有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只留下我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我挑这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说不定也能做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看像什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪兽的恒齿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,锯齿怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,业火熊熊的地狱之门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的都是些可怕的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芸芸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说能做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试看才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看迦南吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇气就涌出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一看到那家伙就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到某个男人时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有相同的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说这种感受叫什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是来阻止梁琪大人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看时机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直后悔把你交给那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这里是为何而生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是为了那个小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造出第二个迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,UA病毒将那个小姑娘的联觉升华到了新境界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们被迫走上了迦南的老路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了为人的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沦为丑陋而扭曲的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不是迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所爱的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所爱的村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所爱的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是无辜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正义必胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想赎罪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有悲剧和泪水的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒那个怪物的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我并肩作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为消失的村民们献上凭吊的鲜花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让迦南的鲜血之花在「{\1c&H00FF00}花园{\r}」盛开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南可能确实是开端
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我们落得这个下场的是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南为了保护重要之人而战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和只会夺人所爱的你们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要保护自己的重要之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我的声音会使人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能听到我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不代表我也能听到你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音通过空气振动传播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影响对方的脑髓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想听那种危险的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不担心这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想回消失的村庄时我就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想守护的幸福岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是囚禁她的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若能忘记这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受我方的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带走那个女人也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人是重要的愚者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要现在杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就万事大吉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想上她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的声音可是剧毒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在床上的娇吟也听不成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连爱的嘤嘤细语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都意味着你的死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱的嘤嘤细语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯肯定希望我能赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放任那群笨蛋逍遥的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能会爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这座研究设施里有很多机关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墙上会「哔哔哔」地射出激光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地板上会「唰」地射出长矛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天花板会「咚」地塌下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经很可怜你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有任何宝贵之物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能独自走向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地板下射长矛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悬吊天花板？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你漫画看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都笑出眼泪来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙耳朵流血了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是把你打入不幸深渊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就亲口告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说…一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再…说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个装模作样的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还敢说什么赎罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哈柯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫外线100%阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的声音也能完全遮断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra violet & noise cancelling helmet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚者还想谈情说爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还早一万两千年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是一件道具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用来制裁迦南的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主动式噪音控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用波形相反的声音抵消原声的设备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要启动这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除一人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都不会受到哈柯的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人就是把一种感觉转换成另一种的迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在无声的世界中心呼唤爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您指引我
