Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南的联觉把声音转换成气味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把颜色转换成听觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五感相互关联
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也能敏锐感知到哈柯的悲叹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将其再转换成声音伤害自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须和过去做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有个万一…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请带哈柯走出这场噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴上这个感觉好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又没有夸你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里真是花园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既阴暗又潮湿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不像开花的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然叫「{\1c&H00FF00}花园{\r}」但哪里都没有花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了个不得了的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和冰箱一个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰面碎了很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道不穿高跟鞋来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
